# Filament Rules

- Keep Filament Resources focused on UI/state orchestration only.
- Delegate domain actions to application services/handlers.
- Add authorization gates/policies for pages, resources, actions, and bulk actions.
- Scope queries to current tenant context by default.
- Prefer reusable form/table components and avoid duplicated schemas.
- Validate server-side even when Filament client-side validation exists.
